    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3, a true purist\u2019s specification featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example boasts a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is in superb condition, with documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension system that retains its original damping characteristics and bushing integrity. Maintenance is exhaustive, including recent rod bearing service and valve adjustments to ensure maximum volumetric efficiency. Finished in flawless paint with a pristine Nappa leather cockpit, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning enthusiast seeking peak longitudinal and lateral performance.",
