    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E36 M3 is a superlative example of analog precision. The S52 3.2L inline-six remains factory-spec, exhibiting perfect compression and seamless VANOS engagement for a linear power band. Power is routed through a ZF five-speed manual gearbox to a 3.15 limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile engagement and optimal traction. The chassis is impeccably preserved, featuring a refreshed suspension with Bilstein dampers and zero bushing deflection, maintaining the model's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and steering feedback. Finished with forged lightweight wheels and a flawless interior, this specimen is free of mechanical lash, fluid seepage, or structural fatigue. It is a true showroom-grade icon for the discerning driver.",
